Duragloss Marine and RV Cleaner with Mildew Buster is a specially formulated blend of surfactants that penetrate and emulsify to make short work of mildew and stubborn stains on vinyl, fiberglass, tiles and other non-porous surfaces on the boat or RV. It is a quick solution that revives mildew-stained surfaces and makes them look new again. It works great inside and outside of the boat or RV. Use it to remove mildew, oil and grease from exterior fiberglass, or use it inside on vinyl seats or countertops. It's quick and easy to get the boat looking its best for an afternoon outing. Integrate it into the regular cleaning routine to keep stubborn stains at bay. Work in a ventilated area. Spray liberally on surface to be cleaned. Allow to dwell for 1-2 minutes and rinse thoroughly with clean water. Repeat as necessary for stubborn stains. Wash hands after use. Note: Make sure to avoid contact with clothing, fabric, wood, metal and porcelain surfaces. Not recommended for highly polished aluminum surfaces.

Item Name: Green Monster Korean Split Microfiber Mitt
Description:
The Green Monster Hybrid Car Wash Mitt is a uniquely designed wash mitt/pad that helps you wash safely and thoroughly! This innovative design features different lengths and densities of fibers. The shorter, more dense, white fibers expand and hold the suds while the longer green fibers gently agitate dirt and grime on the surface of your car. This combo allows you to glide the Green Monster across the paint, pulling dirt and grime from the surface safely and easily. At 9" x 9", you can place the pad securely on your hand and use it as a wash mitt or place your hand directly on top of the Green Monster and use it as a wash pad.
NOTE: The pad comes out of the bag a little stiff. Get it wet, wring it out, and twist it a few times. This will help the pad loosen up for the perfect stiffness during washing.

NanoSkin Ceramic Boost is a silica-based quick detailer, designed to boost gloss and protection on your paint! To apply, simply spray this product onto a clean microfiber towel and apply to the clear coat. Lightly buff off any excess with a separate clean microfiber towel and you are all set, it is that easy! It can be applied as a stand-alone protection product, or as a topper on an existing coating layer. Just one layer can last up to 6 months! Ceramic Boost features a water-based micro-emulsion formula that can be applied to all exterior surfaces like paint, glass, trim, etc. Not only does it bead water incredibly well, but it will also repel water from the surface, making it more difficult for dirt, mud, and other road grime to stick to the surface. This keeps your paint cleaner, longer. If you are looking to protect your paint or existing coating layer, reach for the NanoSkin Ceramic Boost!

The NanoSkin Crystal Wash will allow you to wash and coat your car with protection in one easy step! Having a hydrophobic form of protection on your vehicle encourages water, dirt, grime, and other contamination to slide away, rather than stick to the surface. Treated surfaces stay cleaner for longer and because dirt doesn't bond as readily, cleaning the car is much easier! With Crystal Wash, you get a high-quality, pH neutral, high-lubricity formula. Simply wash your car the same way you would with any other auto shampoo, rinse off, and stand back to admire the results. This shampoo is designed to work as a stand-alone protection product, or on top of an existing coating layer. It is safe on all surfaces including paint, rims, glass, and plastic trim. If you are looking to clean and protect your car from harmful environmental contamination, the NanoSkin Crystal Wash is a great choice!
